@jpsnover 

Firstly, thank you for your contribution in this thread, you're handling this quite well. 

It seems like it should be fairly trivial to fix this in a fairly consistent manner.

PS > get-command ls -All

```
CommandType     Name                                               ModuleName
-----------     ----                                               ----------
Alias           ls -> Get-ChildItem
Application     ls.exe
```

So Powershell already has a means of identifying if there are multiple commands/functions/aliases of the same name present on the system.

I should think one possible solution would be that in the begin block of a Commandlet where a commonly used alias has been provided, that the system run a check using get-command to see if another variation of that command is present.  

As another possibility or extension, you could add a ParameterSet for the commands that includes the native parameters for the original application. Curl being a rather decent example, there really isn't a lot of collisions between the actual Curl command, and the PS Invoke-WebRequest, even including command aliases.  

```
    PS > (get-command invoke-webrequest).Parameters.Keys | % {
    >>  [PSCustomObject] @{
    >>     Name = $_
    >>     Aliases = (get-command invoke-webrequest).Parameters[$_].Aliases
    >>  }
    >> }
    >>

    Name                                                                       Aliases
    ----                                                                       -------
    UseBasicParsing                                                            {}
    Uri                                                                        {}
    WebSession                                                                 {}
    SessionVariable                                                            {SV}
    Credential                                                                 {}
    UseDefaultCredentials                                                      {}
    CertificateThumbprint                                                      {}
    Certificate                                                                {}
    UserAgent                                                                  {}
    DisableKeepAlive                                                           {}
    TimeoutSec                                                                 {}
    Headers                                                                    {}
    MaximumRedirection                                                         {}
    Method                                                                     {}
    Proxy                                                                      {}
    ProxyCredential                                                            {}
    ProxyUseDefaultCredentials                                                 {}
    Body                                                                       {}
    ContentType                                                                {}
    TransferEncoding                                                           {}
    InFile                                                                     {}
    OutFile                                                                    {}
    PassThru                                                                   {}
    Verbose                                                                    {vb}
    Debug                                                                      {db}
